{"tid":685400,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我去睇西醫佢會同我講熱氣？","createTime":"2018-05-31T11:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T12:35:43.000Z","uid":51408,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a8970debf4a4ae64556605f5ffef902c0cac0047","tid":685400,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"個西醫由細睇到大<br />\n大病小病都係睇佢<br />\n以前細個都唔為意<br />\n係近呢一兩年先留意到<br />\n佢診症嗰陣成日會講中醫terms<br />\n好似我呢幾日喉嚨痛到仆街去睇<br />\n佢會話係咪食太多熱氣嘢啊<br />\n記住飲多啲水，食多啲生果補充vit c<br />\n又會話唔好飲咁多涼茶啊會令到個人好虛<br />\n又中又西咁聽到我一頭霧水<br />\n其實依家中醫係咪已經喺西醫有一定根據同地位？"},{"pid":"64bf7aa3cbbbfe20548ef4500f57a13470812bdc","tid":685400,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"你啲炎症咪即係中醫嘅熱氣"},{"pid":"2d33b66437e3dddae79359e37f43cbb492170456","tid":685400,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64bf7aa3cbbbfe20548ef4500f57a13470812bdc","tid":685400,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"你啲炎症咪即係中醫嘅熱氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"啫係現今醫學已經融合到可以中醫溝埋嚟講？<br />\n真心想知"},{"pid":"91176dd6aa4dd405187a2ba7202041d0f2e5e343","tid":685400,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2d33b66437e3dddae79359e37f43cbb492170456","tid":685400,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64bf7aa3cbbbfe20548ef4500f57a13470812bdc","tid":685400,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"你啲炎症咪即係中醫嘅熱氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"啫係現今醫學已經融合到可以中醫溝埋嚟講？<br />\n真心想知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"應該係有啲中醫嘅理論已經可以用一個科學角度解釋"},{"pid":"24111db21c7b434495e328bb692bb1fc244f03a9","tid":685400,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"西醫唔會比中醫上位<br />\n不過的確有唔少西醫自修"},{"pid":"9799c472f39d731b6797abe2221a1cc4c215fc46","tid